Dear all,

1. Trials for the institute chess team for *non-first years* are to be held
on Tuesday, September 13 in 3 different slots at 10 AM, 2 PM and 6 PM. You
can be present in the slot of your choice.

2. *Freshie Chess Schroeter* (UG & PG) will be conducted on Saturday,
September 17 from 10 AM and this will serve as trials for institute team.

Students selected from these trials will represent IIT Madras in
Sportsfest, Inter IIT and other tournaments.

Venue and time of these events will be mailed separately to interested
students who are supposed to fill this form
<https://goo.gl/forms/IALaCcoVVHHPndUM2> before September 11.

